{"tid":1626463,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"10月3號太古果位巴打","createTime":"2019-10-05T11:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T14:04:59.000Z","uid":78689,"like":42,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6c796ac44f0165a28d2e30916137465462e0e95f","tid":1626463,"uid":78689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:24:00.000Z","msg":"自稱冷氣軍師既你我諗你應該都係連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n10月3號果位<br />\n單拖<br />\n一齊送左個比狗塞住左返屋企條路果個妹妹返屋企<br />\n一齊企係最前擋tg，仲踢走左粒tg<br />\n一齊叫前面冇口罩既人小心，因為就黎放tg<br />\n一齊幫人洗眼<br />\n一齊行左去側魚涌撘黨鐵<br />\n一齊搞笑話用廢老卡所以應該要坐關愛坐<br />\n一齊對眼比tg燻到通紅然後互相恥笑<br />\n果位巴打<br />\n<br />\n我爭扎左好耐，但我真係好想搵返你呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好後悔果日冇大膽d問你拎電話，<br />\n如果你冇女朋友既話，不如我地相認"},{"pid":"5a851570683c84eb71729ae9d27178db00a16d46","tid":1626463,"uid":78689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:24:27.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7366809b8fd06bbf542d6d5761aee09f54300e10","tid":1626463,"uid":78689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:24:43.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"4b4177affab0b18d054c199c13382f51062b9f66","tid":1626463,"uid":78689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:24:59.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"686ccab3fee3a51d156f8511ea8582d6f13b380c","tid":1626463,"uid":78689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:25:22.000Z","msg":"就算搵唔返，不相認"},{"pid":"9b3083b3568b571ec6a0301038129a911426a100","tid":1626463,"uid":78689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:26:00.000Z","msg":"我都要約定你同所有手足"},{"pid":"55e208d952d181723aec0eda5f751468d699dd36","tid":1626463,"uid":12